#### Unreasonably Dangerous Product
Background context: A product is considered unreasonably dangerous if it poses an unreasonable risk of harm to consumers. This can be a basis for strict liability claims.

:p How does the court determine whether a product is "unreasonably dangerous"?
??x
The court would assess whether the paintball gun was unreasonably dangerous by evaluating:
